des: BITPOS Point of Sales app using voice to access data information remotely from BITPOS terminal computer. Store owners capture information on the go while they are driving, taking shower, swimming or any situation where holding a phone is a problem. After signing in to Google SignIn it requires Store ID to get the information. The Store ID is a unique number per store and define by the owner of the BITPOS terminal, a Store ID is required every phrase because store owners can have several stores.
